e9Art - Art Trading Cards (Grotesques, et al)
.
.
.
my ‘professional’ art career began in 2014 with selling art trading cards on eBay. i created and sold over 10,000 1/1 paintings in my 7 years on that platform.

then in 2021 my digital scans of a few of these "ACEOs" went (what was for me) “viral” as NFTs on OpenSea …

which has brought me to this place … exploring AI art and making Digital Art Trading Cards … 

and I’m having the time of my life.

thank you !!!

digital art by e9Art using google colab notebooks and photoshop, July 2022
